metadata.name: The feeling of the wind.
metadata.description:
Both hands waving Ogi fans While dancing in the wind and warm light full of flowers all around , Only I am happy.

The umbrella is just an ornament. Because I want the light to hit my body without the need to obscure the light This moment will last forever.

Even if someone sees It wasn't something other people could understand. 

Similar to being in the midst of nature But it's really just what I created. 

But I believe that one day There will be a day when people will recognize the existence of the wind.

Even today my body disintegrates into dust But this wind will carry my feelings in this moment forever. It's all in my heart.

The wind will be the thing that will carry my feelings for all things to experience. 

Do not be fooled by the lights that deceive your eyes, try to use your heart to touch it.
Can you feel it? 

The feeling of the wind.

3800 x 4600 px
30 MB
